code: export default function mean(values,valueof){let count=0;let sum=0;if(valueof===undefined){for(let value of values){if(value!=null&&(value=+value)>=value){++count,sum+=value;}}}else{let index=-1;for(let value of values){if((value=valueof(value,++index,values))!=null&&(value=+value)>=value){++count,sum+=value;}}}if(count)return sum/count;}
